3. BT PasswordSafe Onboarding: (Final step of the Chef script)

Execute API call to onboard the server to BT PasswordSafe

Steps to follow:

Login

Check if a Asset system with the same name already exists

Create an Asset with System Name, IP address.

Check if a managed system with the same name already exists

If not, create a managed system

1. Select appropriate Workgroup (resource zone) base server creation request location

in

2. Check if Managed account exists on this Managed system.

Create Managed Account (e.g.. Haladmin/Hal1919/Root/Haladm)

2. If exists, skip managed account creation.

if exists, skip managed system creation

If exists, skip Asset creation

Log out